problem_description:
ENTITY PROFILE (JSON):
{{entity_profile_json}}

CORE CONCEPT: '{{core_concept}}'

CANDIDATE MATCHES TO EVALUATE:
{{matches}}

answer_format:
Return ONLY a valid JSON object with this exact structure:
{
    "reasoning": "[1-2 sentences explaining profile, entity_category, and key features]",
    "ranked_candidates": [
        {
            "rank": 1,
            "candidate": "...",
            "relevance_score": 0.95,
            "rationale": "[Brief explanation - 1 sentence]"
        }
    ]
}
Rules: include ALL candidates in ranked_candidates; rank 1 = highest relevance_score; relevance_score must be non-increasing as rank increases; return ONLY valid JSON with no surrounding text.
